ction Paul apostles Jesus founder Christian - Beliefnet.com</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://www.h-net.org/reviews/showrev.cgi?path=26412851621644\">[1]</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Davis, Tom. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://newsweek.washingtonpost.com/onfaith/alan_f_segal/2006/12/the_davinci_code_is_wrong_and.html\">\"Alan F. Segal: \"Son of God\" Meaning Depends on Context - On Faith at washingtonpost.com\"</a>. <i>The Washington Post</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Washington+Post&amp;rft.atitle=Alan+F.+Segal%3A+%22Son+of+God%22+Meaning+Depends+on+Context+-+On+Faith+at+washingtonpost.com&amp;rft.aulast=Davis&amp;rft.aufirst=Tom&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsweek.washingtonpost.com%2Fonfaith%2Falan_f_segal%2F2006%2F12%2Fthe_davinci_code_is_wrong_and.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAlan+F.+Segal\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20100115023616/http://www.wnyc.org/shows/lopate/episodes/2004/08/03\">\"Archived copy\"</a>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.wnyc.org/shows/lopate/episodes/2004/08/03\">the original</a> on 2010-01-15<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-01-06</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rf